## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
Write backend tests in `backend/courses/tests.py`:
- Test that students cannot view unapproved courses.
- Test that only mentors can edit their own courses.
- Test that QuizQuestion answers are hidden from GET queries made by students.
- Test course creation, update, and deletion validation.

### Manual Verification
- Log in as Mentor: Create a course, build a sample module and lesson. Request approval.
- Log in as Admin: Open Admin Panel, view the course and approve it.
- Log in as Student: Verify the approved course appears in the course list.
